    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-05-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-05-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="110" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d110">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Dayton</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 464.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-05-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 13, 1864.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Your despatches from No. 529 to No. 533,
                            both inclusive, and likewise despatch numbered by mistake 634, have been
                            duly received.</p>
                <p>I regret that I shall not be able to see M. Drouyn de l’Huys until too
                            late for the mail of to-day. An answer to some matters of business
                            contained in your late despatches will, therefore, have to be delayed
                            until next week. * * *</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WM. L. DAYTON.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, &amp;c., &amp;c.,
                                &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
